beer.beer_description: Pouring a perfect hazy with a pillowy pav head. The aroma is rich and ripe with a multitude of depths as it warms up. On the palate, you'll experience a smooth big-bodied beer with a perception that is light and Moorish. The bitterness is present and guides you to keep drinking. Although the alcohol is noticeable, it's not distracting or damaging to the experience. Big Juicy Hazy IPA is what you'll get.
